Introduction

DXTEEN (also known as 'DXTN') is a 6 member Japanese boy group under LAPONE Entertainment. They debuted on May 10, 2023, with the single album “Brand New Day”.

The group name “DXTEEN” is short for “DREAM X TEEN”, in which they are aiming for a dream, and growing while expanding (eXtention) and expanding (eXpend) step by step, it expresses the “infinite possibilities” of the six teens who continue to work hard and take on challenges, and it contains the meaning of making dreams even bigger even if time passes and grows.

On August 10, 2023, DXTEEN performed on MCountdown with a Korean version of their comeback song “First Flight”.
